articles.title: U.S. Natural Gas Settles Lower in Choppy Trade
articles.mainIdea: U.S. Natural Gas Settles Lower in Choppy Trade
articles.summary: The Wall Street Journal: U.S. Natural Gas Settles Lower in Choppy Trade. U.S. natural gas futures settled lower in volatile trade, picking up from early lows after midday weather forecasts added some cold to the outlook that had already turned colder over the weekend.

articles.title: Why Instacart (CART) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
articles.mainIdea: Why Instacart (CART) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
articles.summary: StockStory: Why Instacart (CART) Shares Are Trading Lower Today. Shares of online grocery delivery platform Instacart (NASDAQ:CART) fell 2.2% in the afternoon session after the company announced it would end a controversial pricing program and separately agreed to a $60 million settlement with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC).
